###  3. Create Accommodation with token (Host Only)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accommodations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "title": "Finca en medellin 2",
  "description": "A comfortable and modern apartment located in the heart of the city.",
  "city": "Medallo",
  "address": "123 Main St, Medallo",
  "latitude": 6.2429,
  "longitude": -75.5812,
  "pricePerNight": 500000.0,
  "maxCapacity": 4,
  "services": ["WiFi", "Air Conditioning", "Kitchen"],
